name: Women's 'Outlaw' Boots (Guristas)
description:
Designer: Unknown

Straight from the discreet consignments of Intaki Commerce, these boots indicate that the wearer is a true supporter of the Guristas. These tall lace-up boots make a statement of power and dominance in basalt and charcoal gray. When paired with the matching coat and pants, these boots represent the ultimate homage to the Guristas.
